resting consequence that may not be immediately obvious. Putting our high-s=
chool algebra thinking cap on, we can solve for <span class=3D"math inline"=
><mjx-container class=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabinde=
x=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"27" style=3D"font-size: 119.6%; position: relat=
ive;"><mjx-math class=3D"MJX-TEX" aria-hidden=3D"true"><mjx-mi class=3D"mjx=
