stive-mml unselectable=3D"on" display=3D"inline"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.=
w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>m</mi></math></mjx-assistive-mml></mjx-contain=
er></span> and this will give us:</p>
<p><span id=3D"eq-sumki2"><span class=3D"math display"><mjx-container class=
=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" display=3D"true" width=3D"fu=
ll" tabindex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"28" style=3D"font-size: 119.6%; min-=
width: 11.761em; position: relative;"><mjx-math width=3D"full" display=3D"t=
rue" class=3D"MJX-TEX" aria-hidden=3D"true"><mjx-mtable width=3D"full" side=
