<p>Which tells us that the number of edges in a graph is the sum of the deg=
rees of each node divided by two. However, this also tell us something else=
: For any undirected graph, <em>the sum of the degrees of each node will al=
ways be an even number</em>. That=E2=80=99s because we know that <span clas=
s=3D"math inline"><mjx-container class=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=
