<p>If we take the average of the average nearest neighbor degree vector for=
 each node shown in <a href=3D"https://olizardo.github.io/networks-textbook=
/lesson-graphs-degree-metrics.html#tbl-knn">Table&nbsp;<span>10.5</span></a=
>, this would give us the graph=E2=80=99s <strong>average nearest neighbor =
degree</strong> (<span class=3D"math inline"><mjx-container class=3D"MathJa=
x CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabindex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"87"=
